des:
We love to share all that is happening around Boca Raton. Follow us at www.soooboca.com and on all the socials! 

Use #SoooBoca if you are posting locations around town...we may feature you on our feed! 

Have an event coming up? Reach out to us to discuss collaborations and we have advertising opportunities available!

Michele Bellisari is the founder of #SoooBoca Lifestyle and a licensed Realtor with RE/MAX Services Boca Raton.
